at implemented).\n- `D-04`: **pass** (first-task completion integrated into completion logic).\n\n## Verdict\nVERDICT: REJECTED\n\nImplementation should return to execution before simplification, with priority on:\n1. Add full alarm edit flow (view model + UI + tests).\n2. Make wake-check escalation automatically evaluated/enforced in runtime flow.\n3. Implement a user-visible reliability ledger timeline for alarm runs, including success/failure/escalation reasons.\nEOF'","aggregated_output":"/bin/bash: line 1: /home/daytona/workspace/.workflow/iphone-app-factory/reviews/implementation-correctness.md: Read-only file system\n","exit_code":1,"status":"failed"}}
